1
00:00:36,033 --> 00:00:38,733
=Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:38,766 --> 00:00:41,200
=Episode 28=

3
00:00:46,100 --> 00:00:46,833
Good. I like it.

4
00:00:47,233 --> 00:00:47,466
Duan.

5
00:00:47,500 --> 00:00:48,333
You know me best.

6
00:00:48,433 --> 00:00:48,766
Here is what we do.

7
00:00:49,066 --> 00:00:49,966
Go get Zheng Lun for me.

8
00:00:50,366 --> 00:00:51,933
Tonight, we try something new.

9
00:00:53,366 --> 00:00:53,866
Let's drink.

10
00:00:58,033 --> 00:00:58,433
Sir.

11
00:00:58,900 --> 00:00:59,300
This way, please.

12
00:01:03,366 --> 00:01:04,933
Please sit for a moment, sir.

13
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:05,966
Someone will attend to you shortly.

14
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:08,633
No need. I prefer to be alone.

15
00:01:08,833 --> 00:01:09,533
You may leave.

16
00:01:12,666 --> 00:01:13,066
My lord.

17
00:01:13,866 --> 00:01:14,266
Here.

18
00:01:23,366 --> 00:01:24,133
Then enjoy yourself, sir.

19
00:02:01,166 --> 00:02:04,066
Sir, if wine and company are not
to your taste,

20
00:02:04,500 --> 00:02:05,600
we also have fine tea.

21
00:02:06,700 --> 00:02:07,933
Thank you. You may go.

22
00:02:08,366 --> 00:02:08,766
Yes.

23
00:03:31,700 --> 00:03:34,066
(Meizhen House)

24
00:03:51,500 --> 00:03:52,100
What do you want?

25
00:03:52,733 --> 00:03:53,166
I'm looking for someone.

26
00:03:53,533 --> 00:03:54,100
You?

27
00:03:54,666 --> 00:03:57,333
You think anyone inside is someone
you have the right to see?

28
00:03:57,500 --> 00:03:59,100
I'm an eighth-rank constable
of the Enforcement Division.

29
00:03:59,433 --> 00:04:00,166
I'm here on official business.

30
00:04:00,333 --> 00:04:00,866
Who dares stop me?

31
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:03,866
An eighth-rank constable?

32
00:04:04,266 --> 00:04:06,500
The dog in our yard has more standing
than your whole family.

33
00:04:06,833 --> 00:04:08,833
Get lost. Stop making trouble here.

34
00:04:15,333 --> 00:04:15,933
Chang Beiming.

35
00:04:23,266 --> 00:04:25,433
She has been drugged with Bliss Powder,
an aphrodisiac.

36
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:26,766
It is colorless and odorless.

37
00:04:27,100 --> 00:04:28,266
Even a silver needle can't detect it.

38
00:04:28,833 --> 00:04:29,833
Go on, my lord.

39
00:04:30,033 --> 00:04:31,233
Go save the beauty.

40
00:04:42,666 --> 00:04:43,900
Go get your reward.

41
00:04:47,933 --> 00:04:48,933
Still acting tough?

42
00:04:49,566 --> 00:04:51,300
Let's see how I deal with you.

43
00:04:58,266 --> 00:04:58,833
This way.

44
00:05:01,033 --> 00:05:02,466
Still feeling proud now?

45
00:05:03,333 --> 00:05:04,933
Didn't you barge into my manor?

46
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:06,100
So hot...

47
00:05:06,766 --> 00:05:09,033
You got His Majesty to scold me,
didn't you?

48
00:05:12,666 --> 00:05:13,433
What's going on?

49
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:16,133
Go, go.

50
00:05:22,766 --> 00:05:23,833
What is the meaning of this?

51
00:05:26,033 --> 00:05:26,533
What happened?

52
00:05:26,900 --> 00:05:28,300
(Gao Tianxi, Manager of Meizhen House)
Young Duke, what brings you here?

53
00:05:28,333 --> 00:05:29,166
Hand over Shen Bingfan.

54
00:05:29,700 --> 00:05:31,900
Or I will tear Meizhen House apart.

55
00:05:32,500 --> 00:05:32,900
Zheng Lun.

56
00:05:33,500 --> 00:05:35,400
Who is this Shen Bingfan
the Young Duke speaks of?

57
00:05:35,566 --> 00:05:36,400
I don't know.

58
00:05:36,700 --> 00:05:38,366
How could a woman come to Meizhen House?

59
00:05:38,366 --> 00:05:40,600
My fiancée is a female Jinyiwei
of the Northern Bureau.

60
00:05:41,100 --> 00:05:42,433
She came disguised as a man
to investigate.

61
00:05:43,666 --> 00:05:45,566
A fine young gentleman did come
this afternoon.

62
00:05:45,866 --> 00:05:46,366
Where is he?

63
00:05:46,500 --> 00:05:49,200
He is drinking with Marquis Taiping
in a room.

64
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:53,266
Hot...

65
00:05:54,100 --> 00:05:54,933
Hot, is it?

66
00:05:55,100 --> 00:05:56,266
Come on. Let me loosen this.

67
00:06:22,766 --> 00:06:23,333
Young Duke.

68
00:06:24,333 --> 00:06:25,433
His Lordship is only drunk.

69
00:06:25,766 --> 00:06:26,600
If you kill him,

70
00:06:27,033 --> 00:06:28,300
how would we explain that
to His Majesty?

71
00:06:43,833 --> 00:06:44,400
Bingfan.

72
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,833
Chang Beiming, you dare strike me?

73
00:07:02,100 --> 00:07:02,700
Today,

74
00:07:03,566 --> 00:07:05,466
you have declared war
on Duke Zheng's household.

75
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:19,600
Young Master Chang.

76
00:07:21,333 --> 00:07:22,033
Is she all right?

77
00:07:23,433 --> 00:07:24,633
I told you not to act rashly.

78
00:07:24,733 --> 00:07:25,666
But you never listen!

79
00:07:57,533 --> 00:07:57,866
You...

80
00:07:58,333 --> 00:07:58,533
You...

81
00:07:58,733 --> 00:07:59,400
You pervert!

82
00:08:03,833 --> 00:08:04,600
I'm...

83
00:08:11,100 --> 00:08:12,333
I'm a pervert?

84
00:08:13,266 --> 00:08:15,300
After last night, who took advantage
of whom is still up for debate.

85
00:08:16,833 --> 00:08:17,266
You...

86
00:08:17,866 --> 00:08:18,700
What do you mean?

87
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:22,133
What did you do last night?

88
00:08:22,500 --> 00:08:23,500
Don't you remember?

89
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:26,766
(Beiming.)

90
00:08:27,733 --> 00:08:28,766
(I'm hot.)

91
00:08:29,366 --> 00:08:30,233
(I'm hot.)

92
00:08:30,700 --> 00:08:31,800
(Where did you go?)

93
00:08:32,066 --> 00:08:33,433
(Come back.)

94
00:08:35,266 --> 00:08:36,266
(Hold on, Bingfan.)

95
00:08:39,566 --> 00:08:40,466
(Beiming.)

96
00:08:49,366 --> 00:08:50,533
(Beiming.)

97
00:08:51,233 --> 00:08:52,266
(I missed you.)

98
00:08:53,700 --> 00:08:54,633
(Did I...)

99
00:08:56,900 --> 00:08:57,600
Beiming.

100
00:08:58,233 --> 00:09:00,133
Did I take advantage of you last night?

101
00:09:01,100 --> 00:09:01,766
What are you talking about?

102
00:09:03,866 --> 00:09:05,300
Could we have a baby?

103
00:09:06,266 --> 00:09:07,033
What did you say?

104
00:09:09,666 --> 00:09:11,900
Could we have a baby?

105
00:09:15,433 --> 00:09:17,466
Then would you prefer a boy or a girl?

106
00:09:18,500 --> 00:09:19,400
Really?

107
00:09:21,700 --> 00:09:24,866
Oh no. I'm not ready to be a mother.

108
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:31,500
I was joking.

109
00:09:32,566 --> 00:09:33,933
After I gave you the medicine
last night,

110
00:09:34,433 --> 00:09:35,133
you fell asleep.

111
00:09:35,166 --> 00:09:36,066
Nothing happened.

112
00:09:37,033 --> 00:09:38,533
Look at my arm. You slept on it
all night.

113
00:09:39,433 --> 00:09:40,466
Take advantage of you?

114
00:09:42,700 --> 00:09:43,866
You didn't touch me
while you had the chance?

115
00:09:49,533 --> 00:09:51,133
Why would I touch you
while I had the chance?

116
00:09:56,666 --> 00:09:57,500
Good.

117
00:09:58,200 --> 00:10:00,766
My master said nine out of ten men
are lechers.

118
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:02,733
Looks like you are the tenth.

119
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,400
Why does your master

120
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:09,000
keep teaching you things like that?

121
00:10:13,666 --> 00:10:15,833
Still, about yesterday...

122
00:10:17,066 --> 00:10:17,733
I owe you.

123
00:10:18,733 --> 00:10:19,166
Thank you.

124
00:10:21,500 --> 00:10:22,033
Finished?

125
00:10:26,233 --> 00:10:26,666
Feeling better?

126
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:29,700
A little.

127
00:10:31,366 --> 00:10:32,266
Now it is my turn to scold you.

128
00:10:36,433 --> 00:10:38,266
Who allowed you to investigate
Meizhen House on your own?

129
00:10:40,666 --> 00:10:41,833
How many times have I told you?

130
00:10:43,233 --> 00:10:44,500
If not for Guan Yunfeng yesterday...

131
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:48,433
If he hadn't sent word,

132
00:10:51,533 --> 00:10:52,866
you would have been done for.

133
00:10:55,833 --> 00:10:56,500
I'm sorry.

134
00:10:58,533 --> 00:10:59,133
How rare.

135
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:02,900
Baihu Shen actually said sorry.

136
00:11:04,566 --> 00:11:06,100
I told you we need teamwork

137
00:11:06,100 --> 00:11:06,933
and a proper plan.

138
00:11:07,100 --> 00:11:08,000
But you wouldn't listen.

139
00:11:08,433 --> 00:11:10,333
One day, you are going
to get yourself killed.

140
00:11:13,400 --> 00:11:13,933
Young Master.

141
00:11:14,233 --> 00:11:14,733
Get out!

142
00:11:17,100 --> 00:11:18,766
Gao Tianxi, manager of Meizhen House,

143
00:11:19,166 --> 00:11:20,333
has brought steward Zheng Lun

144
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:22,433
to apologize in person.

145
00:11:25,333 --> 00:11:26,533
They dare come here?

146
00:11:29,100 --> 00:11:31,433
Young Duke, I deserve death.

147
00:11:31,733 --> 00:11:32,400
I didn't know.

148
00:11:32,666 --> 00:11:35,600
I failed to recognize your fiancée.

149
00:11:35,933 --> 00:11:36,433
But

150
00:11:36,933 --> 00:11:38,633
it was Marquis Taiping, Yin Xian,

151
00:11:38,766 --> 00:11:39,866
who ordered me to do it.

152
00:11:40,100 --> 00:11:42,300
Had I known Miss Shen was your woman,

153
00:11:42,500 --> 00:11:44,233
I would never have dared.

154
00:11:44,233 --> 00:11:44,633
I...

155
00:11:44,933 --> 00:11:46,266
Your hands will hurt
if you slap yourself.

156
00:11:50,500 --> 00:11:51,166
Take this.

157
00:11:58,233 --> 00:11:58,633
Hands off!

158
00:12:06,233 --> 00:12:06,766
I deserve death.

159
00:12:07,066 --> 00:12:07,666
I deserve death.

160
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:08,833
I deserve death.

161
00:12:09,033 --> 00:12:09,466
I...

162
00:12:09,700 --> 00:12:09,966
I deserve death.

163
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:10,433
Get lost!

164
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:16,433
Young Duke, this was all
a misunderstanding.

165
00:12:16,933 --> 00:12:18,366
It was all Marquis Taiping's fault.

166
00:12:18,733 --> 00:12:20,566
After drinking too much,
he had wicked thoughts.

167
00:12:20,933 --> 00:12:23,200
This servant knew nothing.

168
00:12:23,366 --> 00:12:25,733
Even if he had the courage,

169
00:12:25,833 --> 00:12:28,233
he would never dare lay a hand
on your woman.

170
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:30,766
This matter has already reached
Prince Fu.

171
00:12:31,433 --> 00:12:33,700
His Highness ordered me
to punish this servant severely.

172
00:12:35,166 --> 00:12:35,700
Young Duke.

173
00:12:36,266 --> 00:12:38,366
For Prince Fu's sake,

174
00:12:38,566 --> 00:12:41,166
could we let this matter rest?

175
00:13:09,166 --> 00:13:10,233
Does Prince Fu mean

176
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:14,600
to humiliate Duke Zheng's household
with money?

177
00:13:15,366 --> 00:13:16,233
No, no.

178
00:13:16,866 --> 00:13:19,633
Prince Fu only wishes to be
on good terms with you.

179
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:22,400
He would never mean to insult you.

180
00:13:30,500 --> 00:13:31,566
Go back and tell Prince Fu.

181
00:13:32,366 --> 00:13:33,933
I can let this matter go.

182
00:13:34,233 --> 00:13:35,433
But this grudge

183
00:13:36,933 --> 00:13:38,433
will stay with me forever.

184
00:13:45,866 --> 00:13:46,933
My informant sent a secret report.

185
00:13:47,700 --> 00:13:49,200
Zheng Lun has left Meizhen House.

186
00:13:49,766 --> 00:13:51,500
It's just for show.

187
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:52,700
After what happened with Zheng Lun,

188
00:13:53,366 --> 00:13:54,866
Meizhen House would never
keep him around.

189
00:13:56,100 --> 00:13:58,133
I heard Gao Tianxi gave him some money

190
00:13:58,700 --> 00:13:59,866
and sent him home until things
calmed down.

191
00:14:00,433 --> 00:14:01,133
Calm down?

192
00:14:01,866 --> 00:14:02,933
I think Gao Tianxi

193
00:14:03,233 --> 00:14:04,466
plans to take his head

194
00:14:04,700 --> 00:14:05,866
the moment he leaves the capital.

195
00:14:06,333 --> 00:14:06,933
So,

196
00:14:07,533 --> 00:14:08,900
Meizhen House is definitely
hiding something.

197
00:14:09,400 --> 00:14:10,766
But we don't know enough yet

198
00:14:11,066 --> 00:14:11,733
to make a move.

199
00:14:11,833 --> 00:14:14,433
What if I sneak into Meizhen House

200
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:16,000
as a singer?

201
00:14:16,433 --> 00:14:17,133
Too dangerous.

202
00:14:17,566 --> 00:14:18,133
Then maybe

203
00:14:18,533 --> 00:14:19,933
I go in as a cook?

204
00:14:20,433 --> 00:14:21,700
With my martial arts,

205
00:14:22,066 --> 00:14:23,100
if things go wrong,

206
00:14:23,400 --> 00:14:24,966
escaping shouldn't be a problem.

207
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:27,066
If Hua is there,

208
00:14:27,333 --> 00:14:28,433
I think I will be fine too.

209
00:14:30,100 --> 00:14:30,533
All right.

210
00:14:31,433 --> 00:14:32,666
I will have my informant look into it

211
00:14:32,833 --> 00:14:34,900
and see if Meizhen House is hiring.

212
00:14:35,733 --> 00:14:37,000
Then we split up.

213
00:14:37,500 --> 00:14:38,900
Beiming and I will go after Zheng Lun.

214
00:14:39,866 --> 00:14:40,300
Guan.

215
00:14:40,866 --> 00:14:42,100
You help Hua and Xintian

216
00:14:42,266 --> 00:14:43,033
get into Meizhen House.

217
00:14:43,733 --> 00:14:44,800
Duoyu will keep us connected.

218
00:14:45,500 --> 00:14:46,366
But remember,

219
00:14:46,933 --> 00:14:47,533
be careful in everything.

220
00:14:53,666 --> 00:14:55,233
Show them your best skills.

221
00:14:55,433 --> 00:14:56,866
Take good care of our gentlemen.

222
00:14:57,500 --> 00:14:58,200
Yes.

223
00:14:58,833 --> 00:14:59,433
Go on.

224
00:15:01,833 --> 00:15:03,433
Move faster.

225
00:15:04,066 --> 00:15:04,433
Ms. Jiang.

226
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:06,033
Ms. Jiang.

227
00:15:06,533 --> 00:15:07,300
Didn't you say last time

228
00:15:07,333 --> 00:15:08,600
the kitchen needed an extra hand?

229
00:15:09,566 --> 00:15:10,233
What do you think

230
00:15:10,433 --> 00:15:11,033
of these two?

231
00:15:14,200 --> 00:15:16,266
Where did these two come from?

232
00:15:17,066 --> 00:15:19,666
One is a distant niece from my hometown.

233
00:15:20,066 --> 00:15:21,733
The other is her friend.

234
00:15:22,233 --> 00:15:23,800
Madam, my name is Xintian.

235
00:15:25,066 --> 00:15:26,766
I met her on the road.

236
00:15:27,700 --> 00:15:28,433
Greetings, Madam.

237
00:15:29,433 --> 00:15:30,133
I...

238
00:15:32,166 --> 00:15:34,000
I was once Squire He's kept mistress

239
00:15:34,333 --> 00:15:36,200
from Liang Village, outside the capital.

240
00:15:37,366 --> 00:15:37,866
But then...

241
00:15:38,700 --> 00:15:40,600
His wife found out,

242
00:15:41,033 --> 00:15:42,633
and I was thrown out.

243
00:15:43,333 --> 00:15:44,833
With nowhere to go,

244
00:15:45,066 --> 00:15:46,433
I met Xintian on the road.

245
00:15:47,166 --> 00:15:49,433
She said there was work here,

246
00:15:50,066 --> 00:15:51,133
and that I could eat my fill.

247
00:15:51,400 --> 00:15:52,566
What is your name?

248
00:15:53,033 --> 00:15:54,433
Just call me Hua.

249
00:15:54,733 --> 00:15:56,633
Good. As long as you behave,

250
00:15:56,766 --> 00:15:58,200
you will be treated here

251
00:15:58,700 --> 00:16:00,033
no worse than when you were
a kept woman.

252
00:16:00,200 --> 00:16:01,900
Thank you for taking me in, Madam.

253
00:16:01,933 --> 00:16:03,133
What a sweet tongue.

254
00:16:03,500 --> 00:16:05,033
From now on, call me Ms. Jiang.

255
00:16:05,533 --> 00:16:07,600
Forget the kitchen work.

256
00:16:08,333 --> 00:16:09,233
Girl,

257
00:16:09,233 --> 00:16:10,600
can you drink with guests and dance?

258
00:16:11,366 --> 00:16:12,266
Yes, yes.

259
00:16:12,766 --> 00:16:14,666
Dancing is what I do best.

260
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:16,666
Ms. Jiang, what about me?

261
00:16:17,100 --> 00:16:18,033
I can dance too.

262
00:16:18,400 --> 00:16:19,166
You?

263
00:16:20,033 --> 00:16:21,100
Go cook for the servants.

264
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:33,233
You do have some beauty.

265
00:16:33,933 --> 00:16:37,200
Here at Meizhen House,
you could have quite a future.

266
00:16:37,733 --> 00:16:40,766
But there are rules you need
to know first.

267
00:16:41,933 --> 00:16:44,366
Say what should be said,

268
00:16:44,566 --> 00:16:45,600
and keep your mouth shut

269
00:16:46,066 --> 00:16:47,733
about what should not.

270
00:16:48,533 --> 00:16:51,100
Look at what you should,

271
00:16:51,100 --> 00:16:53,800
and look away from what you should not.

272
00:16:54,433 --> 00:16:55,200
Do you understand?

273
00:16:55,600 --> 00:16:58,433
This place is crowded and very large.

274
00:16:59,033 --> 00:17:01,133
If you ever lose your way,

275
00:17:01,233 --> 00:17:02,433
you may never get out again.

276
00:17:02,766 --> 00:17:03,433
Understood?

277
00:17:03,666 --> 00:17:04,433
Hey, Ms. Jiang.

278
00:17:05,666 --> 00:17:06,600
Stay sharp.

279
00:17:07,266 --> 00:17:09,166
Learn to read the room.

280
00:17:09,433 --> 00:17:09,933
Understood?

281
00:17:10,733 --> 00:17:11,433
Yes.

282
00:17:12,433 --> 00:17:14,433
I'll remember everything you taught me,
Ms. Jiang.

283
00:17:14,566 --> 00:17:15,100
Good.

284
00:17:15,600 --> 00:17:17,300
As long as you earn money for me,

285
00:17:17,600 --> 00:17:19,000
I will treat you well.

286
00:17:19,566 --> 00:17:20,100
Come.

287
00:17:23,833 --> 00:17:24,433
Xintian.

288
00:17:27,766 --> 00:17:28,466
What is it, Hua?

289
00:17:29,166 --> 00:17:31,233
This cursed place is definitely wrong.

290
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:33,366
Then you must be careful.

291
00:17:33,733 --> 00:17:34,433
I'm fine.

292
00:17:34,933 --> 00:17:37,600
I can handle it. You are the one
who needs to be careful.

293
00:17:38,600 --> 00:17:39,600
When you look into Leng Xin,

294
00:17:39,700 --> 00:17:40,300
be careful too.

295
00:17:56,733 --> 00:17:57,233
Who is there?

296
00:17:59,533 --> 00:18:00,733
Miss, please don't shout.

297
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:01,533
Please.

298
00:18:02,733 --> 00:18:03,966
Why are you sneaking food here?

299
00:18:04,400 --> 00:18:05,266
Please don't shout.

300
00:18:05,666 --> 00:18:07,066
I... I only took one bite.

301
00:18:07,066 --> 00:18:08,166
Please don't tell anyone.

302
00:18:08,200 --> 00:18:09,733
If Ms. Jiang finds out,
she will beat me again.

303
00:18:11,433 --> 00:18:13,700
It's all right. Don't be scared.
I won'tshout.

304
00:18:15,233 --> 00:18:16,166
What is your name?

305
00:18:17,166 --> 00:18:18,733
My name is Taozi.

306
00:18:19,500 --> 00:18:19,900
I'm

307
00:18:20,100 --> 00:18:21,500
a singer here.

308
00:18:21,733 --> 00:18:23,000
What a sweet name.

309
00:18:23,666 --> 00:18:24,600
I'm Cheng Xintian.

310
00:18:25,533 --> 00:18:26,433
Xintian.

311
00:18:42,866 --> 00:18:46,033
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

312
00:18:46,400 --> 00:18:49,766
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

313
00:18:50,033 --> 00:18:53,033
♪My heart drifted lost♪

314
00:18:53,033 --> 00:18:56,433
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

315
00:18:57,533 --> 00:19:00,733
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

316
00:19:01,166 --> 00:19:04,500
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

317
00:19:05,100 --> 00:19:07,300
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

318
00:19:07,300 --> 00:19:11,333
♪I've softly let it go♪

319
00:19:11,333 --> 00:19:15,200
♪The vow you made was true♪

320
00:19:15,200 --> 00:19:18,933
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

321
00:19:19,266 --> 00:19:21,166
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

322
00:19:21,166 --> 00:19:25,700
♪And forget at world's end♪

323
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:27,500
♪Embracing memory♪

324
00:19:27,500 --> 00:19:29,866
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

325
00:19:29,866 --> 00:19:33,733
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

326
00:19:33,766 --> 00:19:36,066
♪I wish to let it pass♪

327
00:19:36,100 --> 00:19:41,100
♪And run toward this vast life♪
